 \u003cskill name=\"document\" category=\"action\" tool=\"run_skill\" location=\"embedded:/document/SKILL.md\"\u003eAdd comprehensive GoDoc comments to exported symbols\u003c/skill\u003e\n\n  \u003cskill name=\"explain\" category=\"action\" tool=\"run_skill\" location=\"embedded:/explain/SKILL.md\"\u003eExplain code in detail for understanding\u003c/skill\u003e\n\n\u003c/available_skills\u003e\n\n\n\u003cgoa_documentation\u003e\nRead embedded docs via goa:// URLs. AGENTIC-SDK ARCHITECTURE COMMANDS CONFIGURATION DEVELOPMENT GOALS HOTKEYS ORCHESTRATION-DESIGN ORCHESTRATOR PLUGINS PROFILES PROFILING PROVIDER-CONNECTIVITY PROVIDERS SETUP SKILL-EXECUTION SKILLS TOOLS TUI USER-GUIDE WORKFLOWS\n\u003c/goa_documentation\u003e","IsDelta":false,"ToolName":"","ToolInput":"","ToolCallID":"","ToolResult":""}
